data.description: Welcome to this great home in Pinebluff! On this property you will find a 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom split floor plan home with 2 storage sheds, circular drive, fenced back yard and more sitting on .68 acres. The owners suite offers a walk in shower and a garden tub. This home also has RV hookup in the backyard! Seller will be providing 1 year of CPI Security Services, system already in place. $1,500 PREFERRED LENDER CREDIT
